summary: Take the UNP body and make it acceptable for the wife's eyes.
descriptionHtml:
This is a simple replacer for the UNP Body to cover private parts with Osare Suimsuit with leather texture.

No additional mods are required, but make sure to install this after installing the UNP body replacer.

To install simply copy the Data folder into your skyrim folder. Make sure and replace all files.

Anyone is free to modify this mod to suit your purposes.

Special thanks to Anano for the Osare Swimsuit and Dimon99 for UNP Body replacer
